{"tid":1302983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"KFC暑期工(做過既巴打賜教)","createTime":"2019-07-10T06:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T00:30:13.000Z","uid":155123,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"612bb3b52eb96e957108cb1e71b5fa7856775539","tid":1302983,"uid":155123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"小弟岩岩in完pt，<br />\n經理話做廚房，要著防水既黑鞋(姐係防滑既皮鞋都ok?)<br />\n另外，廚房既日常工作主要係咩，平時冇煮過野會唔會好難上手<br />\n仲有，廚房洗唔洗帶哂帽、口罩同白袍。<br />\n有冇做過既巴打有經驗"},{"pid":"b55c67b507825507e16f41d5990c4ebbd2bd4244","tid":1302983,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:45:31.000Z","msg":"算9數啦，廚房即係俾D阿嬸撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0b368c255edc6ab741cf33a8391c51f53dff87","tid":1302983,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbGvyqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbGvyqe.png&h=d8147e40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYXCdqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYXCdqf.png&h=3fab917f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09d0e2f83f8f7f977bb7a5eb19fe9ce787196aa3","tid":1302983,"uid":155123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b55c67b507825507e16f41d5990c4ebbd2bd4244","tid":1302983,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:45:31.000Z","msg":"算9數啦，廚房即係俾D阿嬸撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"係真唔係呀....<br />\n我見呢排都多學生做收銀果邊，<br />\n得一個阿姨做樓面<br />\n廚房入面睇唔到<br />\n巴打再講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d24f1d4ce1a5c3e6dba241cfb8af0b2891cffad","tid":1302983,"uid":42338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:57:52.000Z","msg":"唔好做，真心<br />\n5年前第一份工都係做KFC廚房<br />\n八成時間洗碗，兩成時間炸嘢<br />\n基本上係來來回回洗碗盤同炸爐<br />\n悶到痴線"},{"pid":"3a6763e0b613ac794007500c852eb5f8c48e669a","tid":1302983,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:10:46.000Z","msg":"有得去收銀就去，廚房廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你大概知點做偷食兩個葡撻就好自己穩位去收銀，唔係就做Q死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c769b0213ac31557268264570b3dce12a3b73219","tid":1302983,"uid":155123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6763e0b613ac794007500c852eb5f8c48e669a","tid":1302983,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:10:46.000Z","msg":"有得去收銀就去，廚房廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你大概知點做偷食兩個葡撻就好自己穩位去收銀，唔係就做Q死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"收銀係有得傾計囉，但係繁忙時間都見到冇停<br />\n廚房仲辛苦d?"},{"pid":"8975c3ee472e65f83539b04e38219887669f111f","tid":1302983,"uid":155123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d24f1d4ce1a5c3e6dba241cfb8af0b2891cffad","tid":1302983,"uid":42338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:57:52.000Z","msg":"唔好做，真心<br />\n5年前第一份工都係做KFC廚房<br />\n八成時間洗碗，兩成時間炸嘢<br />\n基本上係來來回回洗碗盤同炸爐<br />\n悶到痴線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"咁巴打你著咩鞋，<br />\n個經理話要防水既黑鞋<br />\n洗唔洗特登買對"},{"pid":"fd3d8f0ed9a1a0ef16f0217d888e7be66298971a","tid":1302983,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"廚房，特別係炸爐個位，日日係嗰度真係吸油吸到你病，其實你有冇唸過part time要做廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為做得耐嘅都唔會去做廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2d2ce9f914cf343e01d7dc4390be18256ba